https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description:
Whats the best way to steal your best friends girlfriend? Lie to her! But thats just low, nobody would go that far, would they? Nobody but Ant-Man! Its another issue filled with backstabbing, cheating, and the occasional feat of superhuman heroics. And meanwhile, disaster strikes the S.H.I.E.L.D. Helicarrier. Who will live? Who will die? The answers will shock you! 
32 PGS./Rated T+ ...$2.99

https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.title: Irredeemable Ant-Man (2006) #3
https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description:
Downtime! While grieving for the loss of friends and colleagues after a massive attack on the S.H.I.E.L.D. Helicarrier, ANT-MAN returns home to the small town he grew up in--where he gets into some small-time trouble with some small time crooks. Luckily, Ant-Man is just the right size for such an adversary. Also featuring some absolutely rotten things done by our titular hero--thats where the irredeemable part comes in! 
32 PGS./Rated T+ ...$2.99

https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.title: Irredeemable Ant-Man (2006) #4
https://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/sto.description:
Its business as usual as Eric OGrady returns to the newly repaired and fully-operational S.H.I.E.L.D. Helicarrier. Still hiding the fact that hes stolen the Ant-Man suit, Eric decides to use his off hours to do a little practice--unfortunately for him, the Helicarrier has developed a bit of a pest problem and he hasnt learned how to talk to insects yet! Oh, well, nows as good a time as any. 
32 PGS./Rated T+ ...$2.99
